
strategey Design pattern
-----------------------------------------
Question-1 Loan Interest Calculation System (Spring + Strategy Pattern)

Configure beans using @Configuration and @Bean (AppConfig class)

📊 Loan Types & Rules:
----------------------
🏠 Home Loan
----------------
Interest Rate: 7% annually
Formula:
Simple Interest = (principal × rate × time) / 100
🚗 Car Loan
Interest Rate: 9% annually
Additional processing fee: ₹2000
Formula:
Interest + fixed processing fee
💳 Personal Loan
Interest Rate: 12% annually
High-risk surcharge: 2% extra
Formula:
Interest calculated using (rate + surcharge)

🏗️ Class Design Requirements:
-----------------------------------------------
1. Strategy Interface: InterestStrategy
Methods:
double calculateInterest(double principal, int timeInYears);
2. Concrete Strategy Classes:
🏠 HomeLoanInterest
Variables:
double rate = 7.0
Responsibility:
Calculate simple interest
🚗 CarLoanInterest
Variables:
double rate = 9.0
double processingFee = 2000
Responsibility:
Calculate interest + add fixed fee
💳 PersonalLoanInterest
Variables:
double rate = 12.0
double riskSurcharge = 2.0
Responsibility:
Add surcharge to rate before calculation
3. Context Class: LoanService
Variables:
InterestStrategy interestStrategy
Methods:
setInterestStrategy(InterestStrategy strategy)
double calculateLoanInterest(double principal, int time)
4. Spring Configuration Class: AppConfig
Requirements:
Annotate class with @Configuration
Define beans using @Bean:
homeLoanInterest()
carLoanInterest()
personalLoanInterest()
Inject appropriate strategy into LoanService
Support runtime selection of strategy (manual or via qualifier/map)
5. Main Runner Class: LoanApplication
Responsibilities:
Load Spring context using AnnotationConfigApplicationContext
Get LoanService bean
Dynamically select loan type (simulate user input)
Call interest calculation